snippet.title: v6.5 Hot Sands Escapade Trailer — Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
Honkai Impact 3rd is ascending to v6.5 Hot Sands Escapade!
New SP battlesuit Susannah Valkyrie Quicksand debuts!
Story Chapter XXXVI, featured event Meow Town Escapade, and version shop Water's Hourglass will be released! Stay tuned!

Voice Artists:
Seele Vollerei: Mai Nakahara
Susannah: Chinatsu Hirose
